1144 such as housing, employment, transportation and food, in order to address those needs. The
1155 task force must consider experiential learning opportunities for social work students and
1166 law students who assist in the court navigation program to earn academic credit. No later
1177 than December 3, 2025, the task force must submit a report that includes the court
1188 navigation program plan, including a model for a court navigation program for use in this
1199 State, and that includes suggested legislation to the Joint Standing Committee on Judiciary.
